          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1666609647390-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> honey</strong>, <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>sweet & tangy yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1666609654311-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1666609654311-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1666609654311-x700.jpg",
