            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1666609654311-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks (reserve a few leaves for garnish)</p><p>Fluff the<strong> bulgur wheat</strong> with a fork and stir through the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>  – this is your<strong> spiced bulgur</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1666609665030-x200.jpg",
