            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1666609665030-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>halloumi, pepper & courgette kebabs </strong>over the <strong>spiced bulgur</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>sweet & tangy yoghurt</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining parsley leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
